### Hadith 1:227

*Narrated Asma':*

A woman came to the Prophet and said, "If anyone of us gets menses in
her clothes then what should she do?" He replied, "She should (take hold
of the soiled place), rub it and put it in the water and rub it in order
to remove the traces of blood and then pour water over it. Then she can
pray in it."

